<task id="Cleaning Tasks" xml:lang="en-US">
    
    <taskbody>
        
        <title>Inside and Outside Cleaning Tasks</title>
        
        <shortdesc>Cleaning Tasks</shortdesc>
        
        <section>
            <title>Inside Cleaning Tasks</title>
            
            <title>Dust</title>
                <p>Dust all the surfaces before vacuuming or sweeping.  Use the dustcloths that are in the sofa table drawer in the living room.</p>
            <br>
                
            
            <title>Vacuum</title>
                <p>Vacuum all the rugs and carpeting.  Be sure to do the following:</p>
                    <list>
                        Dust before vacuuming
                        Move furniture to vacuum under it
                        Use the attachments to vacuum the stairs
                    </list>
            <br></br>
                
            <title>Sweep</title>
                <p>Sweep all the hard surface floors (Kitchen, Sunroom, Bathroom)</p>
            <br></br>
                    
                       
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <title>Outside Cleaning Tasks</title>
            
            <title>Sweep</title>
                <list>
                    Driveway
                    Front walkway and stoop
                    Garage
                    Back Deck
                </list>
            <br></br>
                
                <title>Rake</title>
                <list>
                    Front Yard
                    Fenced Area
                    Back Yard
                </list>
            <br></br>
                
                <title>Weed the Garden</title>
                    <p>Wait until Mom is home and the two of you can weed together.  Mom will show you which plants are weeds and which plants are keepers.</p>
                <br>
                                        
        </section>
        
    </taskbody>
    
</task>
